snippet.title: StarRupture - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PC Early Access this Autumn! Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1631270/StarRupture/
StarRupture is a first-person open world base-building game with advanced combat and exploration. Play alone or in a 4 player co-op on this ever-changing planet. extract and manage resources, build your factory and fight off hordes of alien monsters.

---
